title: Tin Foil Hat #21: I Killed JFK with Jack O'Halloran and Barry Katz
description:
Welcome to another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. Today, Ryan and I, discuss the JFK assassination with Jack O'Halloran and the movie "I Killed JFK" with Barry Katz. On this episode we discuss...
1) Where debut our new theme song "Tin Foil Hat' by DJ Buddy
2)The Mafia
3)JFK's and the Federal Reserve
4)The Operation 40
5) Who was the Umbrella Man
6) The Babushka Lady
then we welcome Barry Katz to the show to discuss his new movie
I Killed JFK! You can see all the details of the May 31st movie premiere at IKilledJFK.com!
